HEADWORD: Japhetic
<hw>Ja*phet"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or
derived from, Japheth, one of the sons of Noah; <as>as,
<ex>Japhetic</ex> nations, the nations of Europe and Northern Asia;
<ex>Japhetic</ex> languages.</as></def>⟦br⟧
